  "HFCs were causing widespread water contamination": "",
  "HFCs were found to also deplete ozone after further research": "",
  "As CFCs were replaced by HFCs, the growing use of these potent greenhouse gases threatened to add significantly to global warming. The Kigali Amendment uses the Montreal Protocol framework to phase down HFC production and consumption.": "",
  "A student reads that ground-level ozone is a harmful pollutant, while stratospheric ozone is beneficial. How can the same molecule have such different effects depending on its location?": "",
